  <Docs>
    <summary>Describes the component swizzle mapping for a Vulkan YCbCr conversion.</summary>
    <remarks><format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[
## Remarks

`GRVkYcbcrComponents` holds the per-channel swizzle indices used when creating
a Vulkan YCbCr sampler conversion. Each property (`R`, `G`, `B`, `A`) stores a
`VkComponentSwizzle` value that controls how the corresponding output channel is
mapped. Pass an instance of this struct as the `Components` field of a
<xref:SkiaSharp.GrVkYcbcrConversionInfo> when setting up a Vulkan backend texture
with YCbCr conversion.

This is a value type and does not require disposal.

## Examples

```csharp
var components = new GRVkYcbcrComponents
{
    R = 0, // VK_COMPONENT_SWIZZLE_IDENTITY
    G = 0,
    B = 0,
    A = 0,
};

var conversionInfo = new GrVkYcbcrConversionInfo
{
    Components = components,
};
```
]]></format></remarks>
  </Docs>
